title: MUMBLE_REMOVE_VOICE_TARGET_PLAYER

0x88CD646F// MumbleRemoveVoiceTargetPlayer
void MUMBLE_REMOVE_VOICE_TARGET_PLAYER(int targetId, Player player);Parameters:targetId: A Mumble voice target ID, ranging from 1..30 (inclusive).player: The player index to remove from the target.Removes the specified player from the user's voice targets.Performs the opposite operation of MUMBLE_ADD_VOICE_TARGET_PLAYER
